Class MailWithPDFAttachmentTest_Dumbster192

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pdfunit.demo.mail_dumbster192.MailWithPDFAttachmentTest_Dumbster192

  • public class MailWithPDFAttachmentTest_Dumbster192
extends java.lang.Object
    This sample shows how to test a PDF document which was sent by email.

    This example uses the mail testing API dumbster, version 1.9.2.

    Author:
    Carsten Siedentop, August 2014 see https://github.com/rjo1970/dumbster.git
